transforms.code:
FROM    (
                    SELECT  REGEXP_REPLACE(user_mobile_no,'[^0-9]','') AS user_mobile_no
                            ,SUBSTR(user_created_time,1,10) AS created_date
                            ,SUBSTR(user_modified_time,1,10) AS modified_date
                    FROM    dana_dwh.dim_user a
                    WHERE   _pt_cr_month <= SUBSTR('${biz-date}',1,7)
                    AND     TO_DATE(SUBSTR(user_modified_time,1,10)) = '${biz-date}'
                    AND     user_mobile_no IS NOT NULL
            )

FROM    (
                SELECT  REGEXP_REPLACE(alias_value,'[^0-9]','') AS alias_value
                        ,SUBSTR(gmt_create,1,10) AS created_date
                        ,SUBSTR(gmt_modified,1,10) AS modified_date
                FROM    dana_dwh.ods_cu_access_token_alias_his
                WHERE   _pt_cr_month <= substr('${biz-date}',1,7)
                AND     TO_DATE(SUBSTR(gmt_modified,1,10)) = '${biz-date}'
                AND     alias_value IS NOT NULL
            )

FROM    (
                SELECT  REGEXP_REPLACE(alias_value,'[^0-9]','') AS alias_value
                        ,SUBSTR(gmt_create,1,10) AS created_date
                        ,SUBSTR(gmt_modified,1,10) AS modified_date
                FROM    dana_dwh.ods_cu_access_token_alias
                WHERE   _pt_cr_month <= substr('${biz-date}',1,7)
                AND     TO_DATE(SUBSTR(gmt_modified,1,10)) = '${biz-date}'
                AND     alias_value IS NOT NULL
            )

from (
        SELECT  REGEXP_REPLACE(receiver_mobile_no,'[^0-9]','')  as receiver_mobile_no
                    ,SUBSTR(created_time,1,10) AS created_date
                    ,SUBSTR(modified_time,1,10) AS modified_date
            FROM    dana_dwh.fact_fund_order 
            WHERE   _pt_cr_date = '${biz-date}'
            and     SUBSTR(modified_time,1,10) = '${biz-date}'
            AND     fund_type IN ('TRANSFER_P2P','TRANSFER_P2L')
            AND     fund_order_status = 'SUCCESS'
            AND     (receiver_mobile_no IS NOT NULL or receiver_mobile_no <> '') 
    )

FROM    (
                -- dim_user source
                SELECT  phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    dim_user_source
                UNION DISTINCT 
                -- bzc source
                SELECT  phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    bzc_source
                UNION DISTINCT
                -- token_alias_his source
                SELECT  phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    token_alias_his
                UNION DISTINCT
                -- token_alias source
                SELECT  phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    token_alias
                UNION DISTINCT
                -- edge_phonebook_contact source
                SELECT phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    edge_phonebook_contact
                UNION DISTINCT
                 -- p2p_mobile_no source
                SELECT phone_number, created_date, modified_date
                FROM    p2p_mobile_no
            )

FROM    today a
LEFT JOIN master b
ON      a.phone_number = b.phone_number

CASE    WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,3) = '62-' THEN user_mobile_no
                WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2) = '62' THEN CONCAT(SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2),'-',SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,3))
                WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2) = '08' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,2))
                ELSE CONCAT('62-',user_mobile_no)
        END

CASE    WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,3) = '62-' THEN user_mobile_no
                WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2) = '62' THEN CONCAT(SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2),'-',SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,3))
                WHEN SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,1,2) = '08' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(user_mobile_no,2))
                ELSE CONCAT('62-',user_mobile_no)
        END

CASE    WHEN SUBSTR(TRIM(mobile_no),1,3) = '+62' THEN SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(mobile_no,'[^0-9]',''),3)
